Greg Hardy was suspended from 10 games by the NFL after he was convicted of domestic abuse last year . 
  The Dallas Cowboys star was seen trying to drive his Bentley through flash floods in Dallas . 
  He was forced to abandon the car and was later seen in another luxury car . 
  Hardy was convicted last July of beating, strangling and threatening to kill ex-girlfriend Nicki Holder  . 
  He was signed by the Cowboys and suspended for 10 games at the start of the season . 
 